# Home-manager-generated files. $XDG_CONFIG_HOME is this repo, so HM writes
# its generated symlinks into the working tree. They point into /nix/store and
# change on every `darwin-rebuild switch`, so they must never be committed
# (a committed store path gets GC'd and dangles on other machines).
# Source of truth: darwin/modules/home.nix
git/config
git/work.inc
jj/config.toml
jj/conf.d/work.toml

